<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL5">
<l>peṇṭirāṟ cukaṅka ḷuyppāṉ periyatō riṭumpai pūṇṭu</l>
<l>uṇṭirāk kiṭakkumpō tuṭalukkē karaintu naintu</l>
<l>taṇṭuḻāy mālai mārpaṉ tamarkaḷāyp pāṭi yāṭit</l>
<l>toṇṭupūṇ ṭamuta muṇṇāt toḻumparcō ṟukakku māṟē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O the way the base people,</l>
<l rend="indent">Who, not undertaking devoted service,</l>
<l rend="indent">dancing, singing, [nor] becoming His people</l>
<l rend="indent">—of Him with a chest with cool tulsi garlands—</l>
<l>do not taste the nectar</l>
<l>[but] enjoy food</l>
<l>becoming yoked with a great evil in order to enjoy pleasures through women [and]</l>
<l>weeping [and] feeling pity for the body when lying down at night having eaten!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
